<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <h3>Help</h3>
    <p>
      Compose or paste your Message Template into the text fields above. You have the option
      of including autofill variables that will automatically be inserted when this Message
      Template is used. Examples of these variables are listed to the right. The availability
      of the autofill variables depend on context.
    </p>
    <p>
      <em>The opening "{{" and closing "}}" braces are required. </em>
    </p>
   </div>
